original_title: Drive-By Truckers: Live at Blue Ox Festival
overview: Drive-By Truckers brave the heat, the wind and the rain at 2017's Blue Ox Festival in Eau Claire, Wisconsin to bring some high-brow Country Rock to the masses. Highlights include: "Ramon Casiano", "Shit Shots Count", "What it Means" and more.
title: Drive-By Truckers: Live at Blue Ox Festival
